eu.webtoolkit.jwt
Class WTableColumn

java.lang.Object
  eu.webtoolkit.jwt.WObject
      eu.webtoolkit.jwt.WTableColumn

public class WTableColumn
extends WObject

A column in a WTable

A WTableColumn is returned by WTable.getColumnAt(int column) and managing various properties of a single column in a table (it is however not a widget).

You cannot access table cells through the column. Instead, to access table cells, see WTable.getElementAt(int row, int column).

A table column corresponds to the HTML <col> tag.

See Also:
WTable, WTableRow
